{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/2012/06/12/limit-selected-items-on-sitecore-multilist-field/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>Problem</h2>\n<p>You want to limit the number of items a user can choose for a multilist field in a data template in sitecore.</p>\n<h2>Solution</h2>\n<p>The solution is easy enough.  Just add some validation to the field that will “count” the number of GUIDs in the raw value of the MultiList field.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open up the template in the tree navigation and click on the MultiList field you want to limit\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 202px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/930fe0afe4f6de714b8af5121845ac69/2e687/sitecore_template_property_nav.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 122.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sitecore_template_property_nav\"\n        title=\"sitecore_template_property_nav\"\n        src=\"/static/930fe0afe4f6de714b8af5121845ac69/2e687/sitecore_template_property_nav.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/930fe0afe4f6de714b8af5121845ac69/772e8/sitecore_template_property_nav.png 200w,\n/static/930fe0afe4f6de714b8af5121845ac69/2e687/sitecore_template_property_nav.png 202w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 202px) 100vw, 202px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>Scroll down to the Validation field and enter this: ^({<sup id=\"fnref-}\"><a href=\"#fn-}\" class=\"footnote-ref\">}</a></sup>+}|?){0,5}$.  This regular expression simply makes sure you have between 0 and 5 GUIDs in the value of the MultiList, effectively limiting the number of items you select in the list.  The {0,5} is the range.  So, change the 0 to limit the lower bound and change the 5 to limit the upper bound.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 333px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/76a41e670dfafb4f0f804c3bc7eca731/24c7e/sitecore_template_validation_field.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sitecore_template_validation_field\"\n        title=\"sitecore_template_validation_field\"\n        src=\"/static/76a41e670dfafb4f0f804c3bc7eca731/24c7e/sitecore_template_validation_field.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/76a41e670dfafb4f0f804c3bc7eca731/772e8/sitecore_template_validation_field.png 200w,\n/static/76a41e670dfafb4f0f804c3bc7eca731/24c7e/sitecore_template_validation_field.png 333w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 333px) 100vw, 333px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>Enter an appropriate message that explains why the validation failed in the ValidationText field.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 610px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c5684b4895855693caa3064a2c04d479/5aae9/sitecore_template_validationtext_field.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAFCAYAAABFA8wzAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAcElEQVQY063NvQ6DIABFYd7/GSU2FeVfgcUGMac4dOjY1Jt8y12OeE6KSSm0sYS44kNk3RIpF7aUfyaklAxyYBwfaG3Qy4KaZ0IIxB5wzncOcwX7Z63Fe8++v6jHQa31i+DmidYaH+d5/k3kUsj5Pm/BSoJ8PpwfzwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sitecore_template_validationtext_field\"\n        title=\"sitecore_template_validationtext_field\"\n        src=\"/static/c5684b4895855693caa3064a2c04d479/5aae9/sitecore_template_validationtext_field.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c5684b4895855693caa3064a2c04d479/772e8/sitecore_template_validationtext_field.png 200w,\n/static/c5684b4895855693caa3064a2c04d479/e17e5/sitecore_template_validationtext_field.png 400w,\n/static/c5684b4895855693caa3064a2c04d479/5aae9/sitecore_template_validationtext_field.png 610w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 610px) 100vw, 610px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/2012/06/12/limit-selected-items-on-sitecore-multilist-field/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Limit Selected Items on Sitecore Multilist Field","formattedDate":"Tue Jun 12th 2012","isoDate":"2012-06-12T00:00:00.000Z","fromNowDate":"10 years ago","categories":["programming"],"tags":["sitecore"]}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Ben Ramey's Blog","tagline":"Scripture, programming problems, solutions and stories."}},"sitePage":{"path":"/dev-404-page/"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2012/06/12/limit-selected-items-on-sitecore-multilist-field/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}